About Huntington Place Apartments
Located in the rural community of Essexville, Huntington Place Apartments is just minutes from the city. Huntington Place Apartments offers beautiful one and two bedroom apartments along with laundry facilities located in each building for your convenience. Enjoy the refreshing pool or maybe you would prefer to bring a book and just relax on the deck. We boast a vast amount of green space, where there are grills and picnic tables located throughout for your pleasure. Community events are offered during the year; which are a wonderful way to get to know your neighbors! There are numerous areas for walking and jogging both in and around Huntington Place Apartments and we are situated right next to the Bay County Riverwalk and Railtrail where in addition to walking or jogging you can also enjoy biking and rollerblading. Huntington Place Apartments invites you to bring your dog or cat with you when you join our community! Our professional and courteous maintenance and leasing staff work hard to create a home that you can be proud of. Give us a call at (844) 841-9037 to schedule your appointment. If you prefer, just stop in and see why when you are a resident of Huntington Place Apartments, you can Expect the Best!



