The Huntington Place Apartments in Essexville, MI | Edward Rose & Sons














































Huntington Place

837 N. Scheurmann Road
Essexville, MI 48732

(844) 546-1432

You are hereHomeHuntington Place 




ENJOY YOUR FIRST MONTH FREE WHEN YOU MOVE INTO A ONE OR TWO BEDROOM LEGACY STYLE APARTMENT!  THIS SPECIAL APPLIES TO 12 MONTH LEASES AND YOU MUST MOVE IN BY SEPTEMBER 1, 2017 IN ORDER TO QUALIFY!  HURRY IN TODAY AND LET US SHOW YOU YOUR NEW HOME!
Located in the rural community of Essexville, Huntington Place Apartments is just minutes from the city. Huntington Place Apartments offers beautiful one and two bedroom apartments along with laundry facilities located in each building for your convenience. Enjoy the refreshing pool or maybe you would prefer to bring a book and just relax on the deck. We boast a vast amount of green space, where there are grills and picnic tables located throughout for your pleasure. Community events are offered during the year; these are a wonderful way to get to know your neighbors! There are numerous areas for walking and jogging both in and around Huntington Place Apartments and it is a short distance to the Rail Trail where in addition to walking or jogging you can also enjoy biking and rollerblading. Huntington Place Apartments invites you to bring your dog or cat with you when you join our community! Our professional and courteous maintenance and leasing staff work hard to create a home that you can be proud of. Give us a call at (844) 546-1432 to schedule your appointment. If you prefer, just stop in and see why when you are a resident of Huntington Place Apartments, you can Expect the Best!
 Highlights Include:

Online Rent Payment Option
Community Gardens
Efficient Gas Heat
Laundry Facilities

 


